Programing Guidlines:
=========================================================================================================================================

1) TradingClient.php implements accessing the trading server. It provides all required function calls which are needed by your trading task. 
please refer to the file for more detailed description of each web service query.

2) please read through trading.robot.php to understand all steps in product trading.

3) modify trading.strategy.php to setup your own trading strategy.
IMPORTANT: 
	1) rename trading.strategy.php, e.g. my.trading.strategy.php
	2) modify trading.robot.php by changing "require_once "./trading.strategy.php" to "require_once "./my.trading.strategy.php". This line is at the very begining of the file
	3) the data structure of the server response is explained when it shows up in the first time.


